San_Buenaventura_(Ventura).Ortonville, California: Ortonville is an archaic Populated Place name in an unincorporated community of Ventura County, California, United States. Ortonville is located along California State Route 33 4.8 miles (7.7 km) northwest of Ventura. Ortonville lies north of the unincorporated community Wadstrom and South of the unincorporated community Weldons.
